OL,4,C'must urgently improve customer
OL,5,Cservice'
OL,7,Fmust "urgently" improve their customer
OL,8,Fservice after a survey found they are
OL,9,Fthe worst energy suppliers for
OL,10,Fresponding quickly and effectively to
OL,11,Fproblems, Which? said.
OL,13,FThe watchdog said "all too often"
OL,14,Fconsumers were being left on hold,
OL,15,Fstuck in never-ending chatbot loops or
OL,16,Fpassed from department to department
OL,17,Fwith no resolution or helpful answer
OL,18,Fto their query.
