OL,4,C'must urgently improve customer
OL,5,Cservice'
OL,7,FEnergy is currently the worst
OL,8,Fperforming sector for customer
OL,9,Fservice, according to Which?'s 2023
OL,10,Fcustomer service survey. That is
OL,11,Fparticularly unacceptable when soaring
OL,12,Fbills have driven the cost-of-living
OL,13,Fcrisis and led to "huge" profits for
OL,14,Fmany suppliers, the consumer group
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FScottish Power, Ovo Energy and British
OL,18,FGas were the worst performing energy
OL,19,Ffirms for quick responses and
OL,20,Feffective solutions to customer
OL,21,Fproblems, the survey found.
