OL,7,FOne British Gas customer told how she
OL,8,Fspent 43 hours on the phone and sent
OL,9,F24 emails trying to fix a billing
OL,10,Fissue for more than a year. She said
OL,11,Fstaff lacked empathy, causing her
OL,12,Fdistress as she was made to repeatedly
OL,13,Fexplain that her husband had died.
OL,15,FAnother found himself stuck at 830th
OL,16,Fin the queue for an online chat after
OL,17,Fstruggling to find any phone numbers
OL,18,Ffor British Gas customer service.
